{"tid":1722750,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[推推推］荃灣悅來酒店嗰對陳詹聯婚嘅新人唔係狗","createTime":"2019-11-15T03:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T05:00:38.000Z","uid":233520,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c2419a9397d2042691b60c78d9f877a9811aec01","tid":1722750,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:41:09.000Z","msg":"大家好，借左朋友acc.新手上路.<br />\n<br />\n頭先見到有手足話要賀下有狗喺荃灣悅來結婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFrt5gh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFrt5gh.jpg&h=a1c3e174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想幫我朋友澄清返。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">陳詹對新人唔係狗。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">佢地係黃絲嫁</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好支持場運動，成日幫手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">喺亂世上結婚好需要勇氣。我好憎狗，好想佢地有報應。但我希望我對黃絲朋友幸福快樂</span><br />\n<br />\n請各位手足幫我推！<br />\n<br />\n我用全家擔保我所講嘅係真，否則我真係死全家！"},{"pid":"d58fc97f924d4f74aff69a9dcf0eab266fb244db","tid":1722750,"uid":282490,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:43:04.000Z","msg":"證據？"},{"pid":"6cb0a011f20d69d0ac7cd5444f12e021f9d7b533","tid":1722750,"uid":140369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:45:27.000Z","msg":"請提出要有力證據"},{"pid":"fd8547c4b09182303ab726d84f4094dbb245544a","tid":1722750,"uid":48604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"冇證據當fake news"},{"pid":"9e9a4502638a835b84d7b519a08d958fb196cb09","tid":1722750,"uid":85478,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:47:18.000Z","msg":"邊撚個話搞五樓，自己衝出黎柒<br />\n搞七樓呀<br />\n此地無銀仲撚on9, 引尻人搞"},{"pid":"fb2660b84196265cfec395e40956db06697bbc5c","tid":1722750,"uid":85478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:47:45.000Z","msg":"我係新人真係多撚得你個豬隊友唔少"},{"pid":"1f2702ba69cbfd92fa381b5a161e3d8f3785d612","tid":1722750,"uid":94958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:49:38.000Z","msg":"又鳩噏？"},{"pid":"9bb9db933274b4b1b0b368dbe720550fc3d23708","tid":1722750,"uid":233520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"我知大家要求證。坦白講我frd好少喺社交媒體上發言。我而家都班緊人去揾proof俾大家。<br />\n<br />\n我都係慎防有手足搞錯左，誤認左佢地係狗。所以先跑出嚟澄清"},{"pid":"b7b82a01c6390d01344a94f5ea89a65113eae9f7","tid":1722750,"uid":106954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:56:25.000Z","msg":"貼佢地工作證咪得"},{"pid":"0caa0e8975647e2d15d47fc2a6eda5ac33f36292","tid":1722750,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"就係無工作證。同埋問過人可唔可以拎卡片做證。但又驚佢地公司唔鍾意佢地拎依啲post 連登"},{"pid":"6aef7fe934757a34a5c8e657592344c3d67001fe","tid":1722750,"uid":139322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb2660b84196265cfec395e40956db06697bbc5c","tid":1722750,"uid":85478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:47:45.000Z","msg":"我係新人真係多撚得你個豬隊友唔少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"可能有心既呢"},{"pid":"c2a26218f8339f8f9603384b214133a749916812","tid":1722750,"uid":213978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"好撚簡單知係咪狗啦 去睇下周圍有無狗仔守門口咪得"},{"pid":"ec52373574dd5dac25a9dbaaaae831e2be3c1601","tid":1722750,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aef7fe934757a34a5c8e657592344c3d67001fe","tid":1722750,"uid":139322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb2660b84196265cfec395e40956db06697bbc5c","tid":1722750,"uid":85478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:47:45.000Z","msg":"我係新人真係多撚得你個豬隊友唔少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"可能有心既呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:06:49.000Z","msg":"我真心想要澄清件事。我係希望手足唔好誤傷。可能關心者亂，所以做得唔夠好。請指教"},{"pid":"03cc852eccbb5d643433f969ad595c228fa6b59f","tid":1722750,"uid":48679,"like":0,"disl